《'''神魂颠倒'''》（{{lang-en|''Head Over Heels''}}）是杰夫·富兰克林创作的美国电视[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]，1997年8月26日至10月28日在[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]播出。节目主要演员包括彼得·道博森、米歇尔·维特菲尔德、[[伊芙·拉茹|伊芙·拉茹]]、[[帕特里克·布里斯托|帕特里克·布里斯托]]和[[辛迪·安布赫尔|辛迪·安布赫尔]]，剧情围绕佛罗里达州[[迈阿密海滩|迈阿密海滩]]的同名[[婚姻介紹所|婚姻介紹所]]展开，其中道博森和维特菲尔德分别饰演合伙开办婚介所的杰克·鲍德温与沃伦·鲍德温兄弟，另外几位演员扮演婚介所雇员。[[康妮·史蒂文斯|康妮·史蒂文斯]]原计划饰演鲍德温兄弟的母亲，但在[[電視試播|试播集]]剧本重写后始终没有在剧中露面。安德鲁·戈特利布是电视剧制作人，张文斯和本·蒙塔尼奥是顾问制作人。

《神魂颠倒》在1997至1998年电视季[[尼爾森NV|尼爾森NV]]追踪的所有电视节目中收视率垫底。联合派拉蒙电视网的宣传主要面向非裔美国观众，为此评论文章质疑剧中何以连黑人主角都没有。本季美国共有多达30个电视剧节目包含{{lang|en|[[LGBT|LGBT]]}}角色，《神魂颠倒》也在其中。节目所获评价不佳，评论员主要批评剧中人物塑造和性幽默。

== 构想和人物 ==
“神魂颠倒”是位于佛罗里达州[[迈阿密海滩|迈阿密海滩]]<ref name="Source2">{{cite web | url = https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1997-08-26-9708250726-story.html | title = UPN Goes On The Offensive With Its 2 Foul And Repulsive Sitcoms UPN | last = Boedeker | first = Hal | date = 1997-08-26 | website = Orlando Sentinel | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040120/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1997-08-26/lifestyle/9708250726_1_esposito-hitz-andrew-dice-clay}}</ref>的视频[[婚姻介紹所|婚姻介紹所]]，由杰克·鲍德温（{{lang|en|Jack Baldwin}}，彼得·道博森饰）和沃伦·鲍德温（{{lang|en|Warren Baldwin}}，米歇尔·维特菲尔德饰）两兄弟合伙经营<ref name="Source9">{{cite web | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | title = UPN Stoops To Conquer Good Taste | last = Carman | first = John | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728035845/https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/UPN-Stoops-To-Conquer-Good-Taste-2829788.php | newspaper = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | date = 1997-08-25 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/UPN-Stoops-To-Conquer-Good-Taste-2829788.php | archive-date = 2018-07-28}}</ref><ref name="Source1">{{cite journal | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no | url = https://variety.com/1997/tv/reviews/head-over-heels-3-1200450610/ | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | title = Head Over Heels | last = Sandler | first = Adam | date = 1997-08-26 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040044/https://variety.com/1997/tv/reviews/head-over-heels-3-1200450610/}}</ref>。两人在许多方面截然相反<ref name="Source15">{{cite news | archive-date = 2018-10-04 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.deseret.com/1997/5/21/19313316/upn-adds-4-more-sitcoms | title = UPN adds 4 more sitcoms | last = Pierce | first = Scott D. | date = 1997-05-21 | newspaper = Deseret News | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181004062608/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/561783/UPN-adds-4-more-sitcoms.html}}</ref>，沃伦对经营婚介所更加上心<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source4">{{cite news | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1997/08/25/upn-fall-scoreboard-1-hit-2-misses/9c678d0f-0658-41dc-a443-b314c7cb1128/ | title = UPN Fall Scoreboard: 1 Hit, 2 Misses | last = Shales | first = Tom | date = 1997-08-25 | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040326/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/1997/08/25/upn-fall-scoreboard-1-hit-2-misses/9c678d0f-0658-41dc-a443-b314c7cb1128/ | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，依然爱着与他疏远、而且已经和职业橄榄球运动员有外遇的妻子<ref name="Source6" />；相比之下，杰克更加花花公子，经常勾搭婚介所的女客户<ref name="Source9" /><ref name="Source6">{{cite news | url = https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bs-xpm-1997-08-25-1997237028-story.html | title = UPN specializing in crude sitcoms Previews: If Andrew (Dice) Clay is your cup of tea, you'll gulp down UPN's latest lemons | last = Zurawik | first = David | date = 1997-08-25 | newspaper = [[巴尔的摩太阳报|The Baltimore Sun]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728035854/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1997-08-25/features/1997237028_1_coolio-clay-hitz | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-24}}</ref>。

婚介所还有几名雇员，如情感顾问卡门（{{lang|en|Carmen}}，[[伊芙·拉茹|伊芙·拉茹]]饰）和伊恩（{{lang|en|Ian}}，帕特里克·布里斯托饰）<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source1" />。卡门是研究人类行为与性的[[哲学博士|哲学博士]]生<ref name="Source1" />，自认是[[女性主義|女性主义者]]<ref name="HighBeam7">{{cite news | deadurl = yes | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4396980.html | title = Dating games fall flat in 'Heels' | last = Grahnke | first = Lon | date = 1997-08-26 | newspaper = [[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] | archive-date = 2018-11-18 | accessdate = 2018-11-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181118100308/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4396980.html}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。伊恩是双性人，还是独身主义者，剧中经常有人质疑他的性取向<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source9" />。前台接待瓦伦蒂娜（{{lang|en|Valentina}}，辛迪·安布赫尔饰）精通计算机，曾是脱衣舞娘<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source4" />。[[凯伦·迪奥|凯伦·迪奥]]（{{lang|en|Karen Dior}}）和[[伯尼·克佩尔|伯尼·克佩尔]]（{{lang|en|Bernie Kopell}}）均以现实生活中的真实身份[[客串|客串]]<ref name="Journal1">{{cite journal | last = Frutkin | first = Alan | date = 1997-09-16 | title = The Best Fall Television | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=MmMEAAAAMBAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN | issue = 742 | pages = 55 | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | journal = The Advocate | archive-date = 2021-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210518055236/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=MmMEAAAAMBAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="SourceTVGuide2" />，[[吉米·兰格|吉米·兰格]]是杰克从小到大的偶像，同样在剧中客串出镜<ref name="SourceTVGuide2">{{cite journal | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | url = https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/head-over-heels/episodes/201910/ | title = Episodes | journal = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040405/https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/head-over-heels/episodes/201910/ | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Book2">{{cite book | last = Terrace | first = Vincent | title = Encyclopedia of Television Shows, 1925 Through 2007: F-L | url = https://archive.org/details/encyclopediatele2007terr | year = 2009 | publisher = McFarland | location = Jefferson | isbn = 978-0-7864-3305-6 | page = [https://archive.org/details/encyclopediatele2007terr/page/n663 657]}}</ref>。

《神魂颠倒》的剧情充斥性幽默<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source4" /><ref name="Source5">{{cite web | url = https://www.eonline.com/news/35274/upn-clubs-head-gumbel-s-got-droopy-eye | title = UPN Clubs "Head"; Gumbel's Got Droopy "Eye" | last = Ryan | first = Joal | date = 1997-10-03 | website = E! News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040201/https://www.eonline.com/news/35274/upn-clubs-head-gumbel-s-got-droopy-eye | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-24}}</ref>，《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的[[汤姆·谢尔斯|汤姆·谢尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）为此批评节目是“肮脏喜剧”<ref name="Source4" />。 艾伦·弗鲁特金（{{lang|en|Alan Frutkin}}）在《[[倡导者_(杂志)|倡导者]]》（''{{lang|en|The Advocate}}''）杂志发文，将本剧与《[[老友记|老友记]]》和《[[憔悴潘郎|憔悴潘郎]]》等情景喜剧对比<ref name="Journal1" />。电视剧[[電視試播|试播集]]就有沃伦违反婚介所政策在办公室和女客户做爱的情节<ref name="Source1" />和[[比基尼泳衣|比基尼泳衣]][[時裝表演|時裝表演]]<ref name="Source9" /><ref name="SourceWobbly">{{cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1997-aug-25-ca-25696-story.html | title = A Wobbly Start, That's for Sure | last = Rosenberg | first = Howard | date = 1997-08-25 | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305001813/http://articles.latimes.com/1997/aug/25/entertainment/ca-25696 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-24}}</ref>。后面的分集有杰克利用化名在[[網路聊天室|網路聊天室]]勾引女人的内容，瓦伦蒂娜一度声称，只要给她每周一千美元，她愿意每次取邮件时裸露上身<ref name="HighBeam7" /><ref name="Source14">{{cite news | url = https://www.deseretnews.com/article/579171/UPN-premieres-3-new-sitcoms.com | title = UPN premieres 3 new sitcoms | last = Pierce | first = Scott | date = 1997-08-25 | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | newspaper = Deseret News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040051/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/579171/UPN-premieres-3-new-sitcoms.com | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

== 制作 ==
[[File:Connie_Stevens_Washington_D.C.jpg|left]] | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728041348/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/new-star-sun-roseanne-appearing-3rd-rock-opener-article-1.772968 | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>]]

《神魂颠倒》由杰夫·富兰克林制片（{{lang|en|Jeff Franklin Productions}}）、[[哥伦比亚三星电视|哥伦比亚三星电视]]（{{lang|en|Columbia TriStar Television}}）和蒙特罗斯制片（{{lang|en|Montrose Productions}}）共同制作，杰夫·富兰克林是节目主创人兼[[執行製作人|執行製作人]]<ref name="Source1" />。《[[落基山新闻报|落基山新闻报]]》（''{{lang|en|Rocky Mountain News}}''）的达斯提·桑德斯（{{lang|en|Dusty Saunders}}）在文章中谈及富兰克林之前创作的情景喜剧《[[歡樂滿屋|歡樂滿屋]]》，笑称富兰克林可能是在性题材电视节目上有什么不堪回首而且耿耿于怀的往事，所以这些年来创作出那么多喜怒无常的虚构家庭成员<ref name="HighBeam1">{{cite news | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-67748910.html | title = UPN stumbles with 'Head Over Heels' | last = Saunders | first = Dusty | date = 1997-08-25 | newspaper = Rocky Mountain News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181120135216/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-67748910.html | archive-date = 2018-11-20 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-11-20}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。安德鲁·戈特利布（{{lang|en|Andrew Gottlieb}}）也是电视剧制作人，张文斯（{{lang|en|Vince Cheung}}）和本·蒙塔尼奥（{{lang|en|Ben Montanio}}）是顾问制作人。剧中故事发生在迈阿密海滩，但实际是在洛杉矶取景。<ref name="Source1" />[[马修·戴蒙德|马修·戴蒙德]]（{{lang|en|Matthew Diamond}}）共导演三集，[[阿曼达·比尔斯|阿曼达·比尔斯]]和[[阿萨德·克拉达|阿萨德·克拉达]]（{{lang|en|Asaad Kelada}}）各导演一集<ref name="SourceTVGuide2" />。保罗·巴克利（{{lang|en|Paul Buckley}}）和乔纳森·沃尔夫（{{lang|en|Jonathan Wolff}}）为电视剧作曲<ref name="Source1" />。

节目制作期间，康妮·史蒂文斯（{{lang|en|Connie Stevens}}）原订出演鲍德温兄弟的母亲，属[[常设角色|常设角色]]<ref name="Source7" /><ref name="HighBeam2">{{cite news | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-736467.html | title = UPN Trots Out Three New Sitcoms; 'Clueless' Joins Next Month | last = Hill | first = Michael E. | date = 1997-08-24 | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | accessdate = 2018-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181121020902/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-736467.html | archive-date = 2018-11-21 | deadurl = yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。[[特纳经典电影频道|特纳经典电影频道]]因此声称本剧是重振史蒂文斯演艺生涯的作品<ref name="Source13">{{cite web | url = http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/person/186790%7C0/Michael-Sullivan/ | title = Biography | publisher = [[特纳经典电影频道|Turner Classic Movies]] | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200705123921/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/person/186790%7C0/Michael-Sullivan/ | archive-date = 2020-07-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]本是因史蒂文斯出演而订购《神魂颠倒》<ref name="Source7" />，但之后却因所谓“创意变更”取消她的角色。原本的试播集剧情讲述史蒂文斯扮演的母亲与婚介所老板交往，老板后来把婚介所交给她的两个儿子经营。<ref name="Source7" />身为两个成年男子的母亲，她“胸大无脑”且为人开放<ref name="SourceWobbly" />，与西班牙[[私人教练|私人教练]]交往期间还经常谈论两人的性关系<ref name="Source6" /><ref name="HighBeam2" />。但是，《神魂颠倒》后来取消鲍德温一家与婚介所过去关系的情节<ref name="Source7" />。参演《[[我的孩子们|我的孩子们]]》（''{{lang|en|All My Children}}''）的拉茹因角色不再出场加入本剧，试播集重写后新增她的戏份<ref name="Source7" /><ref name="SourcePeople11">{{cite journal | url = https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-talking-with-vol-48-no-10/ | title = Picks and Pans Review: Talking With... | date = 1997-09-08 | journal = [[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728035956/https://people.com/archive/picks-and-pans-review-talking-with-vol-48-no-10/ | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

