== 播映 ==
[[File:Actor_Patrick_Bristow.jpg|right]]

联合派拉蒙电视网共为1997至1998年电视季订购三部情景喜剧，分别是《神魂颠倒》、《希兹》（{{lang|en|''Hitz''}}）和《[[好消息(电视剧)|好消息]]》（''{{lang|en|Good News}}''）<ref name="Source16">{{cite news | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1997-05-21-9705200218-story.html | title = UPN: Three New Shows, 'Clueless' | last = Jicha | first = Tom | date = 1997-05-21 | newspaper = Sun-Sentinel | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728070947/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1997-05-21/lifestyle/9705200218_1_upn-claude-brooks-wb | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，以满足将每周黄金时间段扩展到四个夜晚的节目需求<ref name="Source8">{{cite news | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1997-05-21-9705210122-story.html | title = UPN Expanding Prime-time Offerings | date = 1997-05-21 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728035705/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1997-05-21/news/9705210122_1_three-new-comedy-series-hitz-united-paramount-network | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-24}}</ref>。联合派拉蒙电视网将《神魂颠倒》的目标观众定为非裔美国族群，但剧中却没有黑人演员<ref name="HighBeam2" />。《行业观察家》（{{lang|en|''industry observers''}}）批评电视台“背弃黑人观众”，“拒绝包含黑人明星或制作人的项目”，对此公司总裁迪恩·瓦伦丁（{{lang|en|Dean Valentine}}）坚决否认<ref name="HighBeam3">{{cite news | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4411189.html | title = UPN denies giving up on its black viewers | last = Braxton | first = Greg | date = 1997-12-20 | newspaper = [[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181120091247/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-4411189.html | archive-date = 2018-11-20 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-11-20}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。

剧中帕特里克·布里斯托（{{lang|en|Patrick Bristow}}）诠释的伊恩是双性人，《神魂颠倒》因此成为该季带{{lang|en|LGBT}}角色的30部电视剧之一<ref name="HighBeam6" />。布里斯托在谈及人物性经历时称，伊恩拥有“色彩斑澜、五彩缤纷的过去”<ref name="HighBeam2" />。社会学家[[苏珊娜·达努塔·沃尔特斯|苏珊娜·达努塔·沃尔特斯]]（{{lang|en|Suzanna Danuta Walters}}）的著作指出，伊恩和情景喜剧《[[薇洛尼卡的衣橱|薇洛尼卡的衣橱]]》（''{{lang|en|Veronica's Closet}}''）中的乔什·尼科莱·布莱尔（{{lang|en|Josh Nicolé Blair}}）代表电视节目新趋势：“同性恋负责插科打诨”，人物就是不肯承认各自的性取向<ref name="Book1">{{cite book | last = Walters | first = Suzanna Danuta | title = All the Rage: The Story of Gay Visibility in America | year = 2003 | publisher = University of Chicago Press | location = Chicago | page = 117 | isbn = 978-0-226-87232-2}}</ref>。

《神魂颠倒》在[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]每周二晚九点半播出<ref name="Source1" />，之前的节目是《希兹》<ref name="Source2" />，原计划在晚上八点半播映<ref name="Source15" /><ref name="HighBeam1" />。本剧的[[美国电视分级制度|电视分级]]为{{lang|en|TV-PG}}<ref name="Source10">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040135/http://www.southcoasttoday.com/article/19970826/News/308269933 | url = https://www.southcoasttoday.com/article/19970826/News/308269933 | title = 'Hitz': New UPN sitcom has feet of (Andrew Dice) Clay | date = 1997-08-26 | newspaper = The Standard-Times | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archivedate = 2018-07-28}}</ref>，提醒家长剧中存在性暗示和露骨情节<ref name="HighBeam7" />，《[[德瑟雷特新闻报|德瑟雷特新闻报]]》（''{{lang|en|Deseret News}}''）的斯科特·皮尔斯（{{lang|en|Scott D. Pierce}}）发文称，本剧包含的性内容很多，评为[[美国电视分级制度|TV-14]]级更妥当<ref name="Source14" />。《神魂颠倒》平均每周仅吸引230万观众<ref name="Source5" />，和《[[好啦_(电视剧)|好啦]]》（''{{lang|en|Alright Already}}''）在[[尼爾森NV|尼爾森NV]]本季追踪的所有节目中并列倒数第一。两部节目的整体观众人数都只有270万<ref name="Source12">{{cite web | url = https://ew.com/article/1998/05/29/what-ranked-and-what-tanked/ | title = What ranked and what tanked | date = 1998-05-29 | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200915220213/https://ew.com/article/1998/05/29/what-ranked-and-what-tanked/ | archive-date = 2020-09-15 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-24}}</ref>。

《神魂颠倒》是1997至1998年电视季第一个被砍的节目<ref name="Source5" /><ref name="Source11">{{cite journal | url = https://people.com/archive/worst-of-tube-vol-48-no-26/ | title = Worst of Tube | date = 1997-12-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728070946/https://people.com/archive/worst-of-tube-vol-48-no-26/ | journal = [[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | archivedate = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。虽已订购13集<ref name="Source5" />，但实际播出的仅八集<ref name="SourceTVGuide2" />。有报导称节目会播出到11月<ref name="Source5" />，但事实证明1997年10月28日播出的第八集就是最后一集<ref name="SourceTVGuide2" />。全部八集都有道博森和维特菲尔德参演，布里斯托出演七集，拉茹和安布赫尔（{{lang|en|Cindy Ambuehl}}）各出演四集<ref name="SourceTVGuide1">{{cite journal | url = https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/head-over-heels/cast/201910/ | title = Cast | journal = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180728040329/https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/head-over-heels/cast/201910/ | archive-date = 2018-07-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-24}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
《神魂颠倒》所获评价不佳。乔尔·瑞安（{{lang|en|Joal Ryan}}）在《[[E！新闻|E！新闻]]》（{{lang|en|''E! News''}}）发文，称本剧刚一开播就已公认为“全季最烂新剧”<ref name="Source5" />。评论主要批评节目的性笑料<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source9" /><ref name="Source14" /><ref name="Source11" />，例如《德瑟雷特新闻报》就批评电视剧充斥“性能力、性高潮和身体机能相关笑料，既粗俗又无聊”<ref name="SourceDeseretNewsMoreandMore">{{cite news | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | url = https://www.deseret.com/1997/9/1/19331554/upn-is-making-changes-but-not-enough | title = UPN is making changes but not enough | date = 1997-09-01 | newspaper = Deseret News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181006193343/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/580396/UPN-is-making-changes-but-not-enough.html | archive-date = 2018-10-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。桑德斯在《落基山新闻报》发文，同样认为本剧是全季表现很差的节目，属于模仿《老友记》但画虎不成反类犬的作品<ref name="HighBeam1" />。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》刊登霍华德·罗森伯格（{{lang|en|Howard Rosenberg}}）的文章，称其他愚蠢的情景喜剧和《神魂颠倒》相比都是小巫见大巫，而且节目一无是处，“轻于鸿毛”<ref name="SourceWobbly" />。也有部分评论看到本剧的可取之处<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source4" />。汤姆·谢尔斯虽认为联合派拉蒙电视网有些看走眼，但剧中幽默还不至于像《希兹》那样“丑陋和恶毒”，他还称赞布里斯托的表演很抢戏，瓦伦蒂娜精通技术的设定也很可爱<ref name="Source4" /><ref name="Source4" />。亚当·桑德勒（{{lang|en|Adam Sandler}}）在《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》发文称赞节目的[[片头字幕|片头字幕]]颇为时髦和刺激，可与罪案剧情电视剧《[[豪门疑案|豪门疑案]]》（''{{lang|en|Silk Stalkings}}''）的片头相提并论<ref name="Source1" />。

剧中人物同样不受待见，特别是女角色塑造颇显[[性別歧視主義|性别歧视]]<ref name="Source6" /><ref name="HighBeam7" />。《[[巴尔的摩太阳报|巴尔的摩太阳报]]》的大卫·祖拉维克（{{lang|en|David Zurawik}}）特别批评剧中瓦伦蒂娜和鲍德温兄弟的母亲，瓦伦蒂娜的塑造基本不离性符号范围，鲍德温兄弟的母亲戏份只剩下与男友的关系，两者都是《神魂颠倒》女角色形象不佳的例证<ref name="Source6" />。桑德勒和《[[洛杉矶每日新闻报|洛杉矶每日新闻报]]》（''{{lang|en|Los Angeles Daily News}}''）的基思·马德（{{lang|en|Keith Marder}}）都感觉剧中人物全靠陈辞滥调支撑<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="HighBeam5">{{cite news | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-83878851.html | title = Season's Best, Worst Shows | last = Marder | first = Keith | date = 1997-09-14 | newspaper = Los Angeles Daily News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181120000019/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-83878851.html | archive-date = 2018-11-20 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-11-20}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。马德的总结认为，本剧纯属“低劣品味和可笑漫画乱七八糟的组合”<ref name="HighBeam5" />。

